          infrared broilers, and professional-grade components.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Accurate Diagnostics:</strong>
          We do not guess. We identify the actual source of the problem so your BlueStar
          appliance repair is handled correctly the first time whenever possible.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Premium Parts & Careful Workmanship:</strong>
          We use quality replacement parts and take care to protect the finish, fit,
          and performance of your luxury appliance throughout the repair process.
        </li>
        <li>
