        <li>Heavy-duty professional-style construction</li>
        <li>Custom color, trim, and design configurations</li>
        <li>Precision cooking performance for luxury kitchens</li>
        <li>Specialized refrigeration and ventilation systems</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Our goal is not just to get your appliance running again. Our goal is to restore
        the performance, control, and reliability that made you choose BlueStar in the first place.
      </p>
